      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>DRKOOP.COM INC., Austin, Tex., the Internet health company, said it had laid off about 35 percent of its staff since the beginning of April.</p>
        <p>BERKSHIRE HATHAWAY INC., Omaha, said it would acquire Ben Bridge Jeweler, Seattle, a family-owned chain with 63 jewelry stores in 18 states. Financial terms were not disclosed.</p>
